data.description: Welcome to this wonderful home in the desirable Bell Farms subdivision. Boasting three spacious bedrooms and an open floor plan, this property provides a perfect blend of comfort and style. The great location places you within easy reach of shopping, dining, and all the amenities south Lubbock has to offer. Whether you're a growing family or seeking a place to entertain and relax, this home provides the space and convenience you've been looking for. Call and set up your private tour now!
